Dependencies:

	x11			(required)
	alsa-lib	(recommended)
	libogg		(recommended)
	libvorbis	(recommended)
	libmad		(recommended)


Extensions:

	samba       (optional)
	arts        (optional)
	gnome-vfs   (optional)
	esound      (optional)


Codecs:

	libdvdnav	(optional)
	flac		(optional)
	libsdl		(optional)
	libmng		(optional)
	liba52		(optional)
	speex		(optional)
	libtheora	(optional)
	faad2		(optional)
